related_properties.title: device_id
related_properties.description: A unique identifier for the user's device.

related_properties.description: Session start time in ms since epoch; shared by all events in the session; -1 = out-of-session

related_properties.title: event_id
related_properties.description: Optional integer counter to disambiguate events with same timestamp.

related_properties.description: Unique deduplication key for an event.

related_properties.description: Amplitude’s internal numeric user identifier on the event

related_properties.description: SDK/library identifier used to send the event

related_properties.description: IP seen at ingestion (used for GeoIP)

related_properties.description: Group dictionary applied at event time

related_properties.description: Dictionary of user-scoped properties applied at event time

related_properties.description: True if last step in flow
